title: Mike Anderson and the Converse Cons Star Player Skate
description:
A day in the life with CONS Ambassador Mike Anderson -- skating, friends, family — with a little help from the Yellow Van. The Converse CONS Star Player Skate sneakers is now available at finer skate shops worldwide. 

Music: Burto Fernl by The Jovontaes
